{"ja261:0.1":"Jataka ","ja261:0.2":"Tikanipata ","ja261:0.3":"Padumavagga ","ja261:0.4":"1. Padumajataka ","ja261:1.1":"“Yatha kesa ca massu ca, ","ja261:1.2":"chinnam chinnam viruhati; ","ja261:1.3":"Evam ruhatu te nasa, ","ja261:1.4":"padumam dehi yacito”. ","ja261:2.1":"“Yatha saradikam bijam, ","ja261:2.2":"khette vuttam viruhati; ","ja261:2.3":"Evam ruhatu te nasa, ","ja261:2.4":"padumam dehi yacito”. ","ja261:3.1":"“Ubhopi palapantete, ","ja261:3.2":"api padmani dassati; ","ja261:3.3":"Vajjum va te na va vajjum, ","ja261:3.4":"natthi nasaya ruhana; ","ja261:3.5":"Dehi samma padumani, ","ja261:3.6":"aham yacami yacito”ti. ","ja261:4.1":"Padumajatakam pathamam. "}